        "custom_liquid": "{% comment %}\n  Beast Armor PBX Product Launch Blog Template\n  Usage: Can be used as a product template, blog article template, or landing page\n{% endcomment %}\n\n{% assign product = products['beast-armor-pbx'] %}\n{% assign current_date = 'now' | date: '%b %d' %}\n\n<article class=\"beast-launch-blog\">\n  <header class=\"blog-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"blog-title\">\n      **The {{ product.title }} Just Shattered Every Expectation – Here's Why Champions Are Going Wild**\n    </h1>\n    <div class=\"blog-meta\">\n      <time datetime=\"{{ article.created_at | date: '%Y-%m-%d' }}\">\n        {{ current_date }}\n      </time>\n      <span class=\"author\">Written By {{ blog.title | default: 'HNDRD Team' }}</span>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <div class=\"blog-content\">\n    <section class=\"hero-section\">\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">\n        The {{ product.title }} Has Officially Landed – And the Court Will Never Be the Same\n      </h2>\n      \n      <p class=\"hero-text\">\n        Forget everything you thought you knew about pickleball paddles. The {{ product.title }} isn't just another piece of equipment; it's a <strong>game-ending weapon</strong> that transforms weekend warriors into court legends and turns casual players into unstoppable forces of nature.\n      </p>\n      \n      <p class=\"cta-text\">\n        <strong>The Beast is here. Are you ready to unleash it?</strong>\n      </p>\n    </section>\n\n    {% if product.images.size > 0 %}\n    <div class=\"product-showcase\">\n      <img src=\"{{ product.featured_image | img_url: '800x800' }}\" \n           alt=\"{{ product.title }}\" \n           class=\"hero-image\">\n    </div>\n    {% endif %}\n\n    <section class=\"features-section\">\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">\n        What Makes the {{ product.title }} the Most Dominant Paddle Ever Created?\n      </h2>\n      \n      <p class=\"intro-text\">\n        This isn't just evolution – it's a complete <strong>revolution</strong> in paddle engineering. Every element has been designed with one goal: <strong>total court domination</strong>.\n      </p>\n\n      <div class=\"features-grid\">\n        <div class=\"feature-item\">\n          <h3 class=\"feature-title\">The Power Core Revolution:</h3>\n          <p>At the heart of the Beast lies an advanced core technology that doesn't just respond to your swing – it <strong>amplifies</strong> it. Every strike becomes a statement. Every return becomes a threat.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"feature-item\">\n          <h3 class=\"feature-title\">Armor-Grade Durability:</h3>\n          <p>The \"Armor\" in {{ product.title }} isn't just a name – it's a promise. This paddle is built to withstand the most aggressive play styles while maintaining peak performance match after match. No chips. No cracks. No compromise.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"feature-item\">\n          <h3 class=\"feature-title\">Precision Engineering:</h3>\n          <p>The Beast's carefully calibrated weight distribution creates the perfect balance between power and control. You're not just hitting the ball – you're <strong>commanding</strong> it exactly where you want it to go.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"feature-item\">\n          <h3 class=\"feature-title\">Elite Performance Surface:</h3>\n          <p>The textured face doesn't just grip the ball; it <strong>controls</strong> the spin like never before. Your opponents won't just struggle to return your shots – they'll struggle to even read them.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"testimonials-section\">\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">\n        What Players Are Saying: \"This Paddle Changed Everything\"\n      </h2>\n      \n      <div class=\"testimonials-grid\">\n        <blockquote class=\"testimonial\">\n          <p>\"I thought I knew what power felt like until I picked up the Beast. This thing is absolutely devastating.\"</p>\n          <cite>– Sarah M., Tournament Player</cite>\n        </blockquote>\n\n        <blockquote class=\"testimonial\">\n          <p>\"The difference was immediate. First swing, I knew this wasn't just another paddle upgrade – this was a complete game changer.\"</p>\n          <cite>– Mike R., Club Champion</cite>\n        </blockquote>\n\n        <blockquote class=\"testimonial\">\n          <p>\"My opponents keep asking what paddle I'm using. The Beast speaks for itself.\"</p>\n          <cite>– Jessica L., League Player</cite>\n        </blockquote>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta-section\">\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">Ready to Join the Beast Army?</h2>\n      \n      <p class=\"cta-text\">\n        The {{ product.title }} is <strong>available now</strong> – but paddles this revolutionary don't stay in stock long. Once word spreads about what the Beast can do, everyone will want one.\n      </p>\n      \n      <p class=\"urgency-text\">\n        <strong>Don't wait. Don't hesitate. The Beast is ready when you are.</strong>\n      </p>\n\n      {% if product.available %}\n        <div class=\"product-cta\">\n          <form action=\"/cart/add\" method=\"post\" enctype=\"multipart/form-data\">\n            <select name=\"id\" class=\"variant-selector\">\n              {% for variant in product.variants %}\n                <option value=\"{{ variant.id }}\" {% unless variant.available %}disabled{% endunless %}>\n                  {{ variant.title }} - {{ variant.price | money }}\n                  {% unless variant.available %} (Sold Out){% endunless %}\n                </option>\n              {% endfor %}\n            </select>\n            \n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"beast-cta-btn\" {% unless product.available %}disabled{% endunless %}>\n              UNLEASH THE BEAST – ORDER NOW\n            </button>\n          </form>\n          \n          <p class=\"price-display\">\n            {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}\n              <span class=\"original-price\">{{ product.compare_at_price | money }}</span>\n            {% endif %}\n            <span class=\"current-price\">{{ product.price | money }}</span>\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      {% else %}\n        <div class=\"sold-out-message\">\n          <h3>SOLD OUT - Join the Waitlist</h3>\n          <p>The Beast proved too popular! Get notified when it's back in stock.</p>\n          <button class=\"waitlist-btn\">JOIN WAITLIST</button>\n        </div>\n      {% endif %}\n    </section>\n\n    <footer class=\"blog-footer\">\n      <hr>\n      <p class=\"closing-text\">\n        <em>Your opponents have been warned. The {{ product.title }} is here, and the game will never be the same. Will you be holding it, or facing it across the net?</em>\n      </p>\n      \n      {% if blog.tags.size > 0 %}\n      <div class=\"tags\">\n        <span>Tags: </span>\n        {% for tag in blog.tags %}\n          <span class=\"tag\">{{ tag }}</span>{% unless forloop.last %}, {% endunless %}\n        {% endfor %}\n      </div>\n      {% endif %}\n    </footer>\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<style>\n  .beast-launch-blog {\n    max-width: 800px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding: 2rem;\n    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n  }\n  \n  .blog-title {\n    font-size: 2.5rem;\n    font-weight: 900;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    color: #1a1a1a;\n  }\n  \n  .blog-meta {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 1rem;\n    margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    color: #666;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  \n  .section-title {\n    font-size: 1.8rem;\n    font-weight: 800;\n    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;\n    color: #1a1a1a;\n  }\n  \n  .hero-text, .intro-text {\n    font-size: 1.1rem;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n  }\n  \n  .cta-text {\n    font-size: 1.2rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    text-align: center;\n    margin: 2rem 0;\n    color: #d32f2f;\n  }\n  \n  .features-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n    gap: 2rem;\n    margin: 2rem 0;\n  }\n  \n  .feature-item {\n    padding: 1.5rem;\n    border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    background: #fafafa;\n  }\n  \n  .feature-title {\n    font-size: 1.2rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #1a1a1a;\n    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n  }\n  \n  .testimonials-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    gap: 1.5rem;\n    margin: 2rem 0;\n  }\n  \n  .testimonial {\n    padding: 1.5rem;\n    background: #f5f5f5;\n    border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-style: italic;\n  }\n  \n  .beast-cta-btn {\n    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #d32f2f, #f44336);\n    color: white;\n    border: none;\n    padding: 1rem 2rem;\n    font-size: 1.1rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n    transition: transform 0.2s;\n  }\n  \n  .beast-cta-btn:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3);\n  }\n  \n  .price-display {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-top: 1rem;\n  }\n  \n  .current-price {\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #d32f2f;\n  }\n  \n  .original-price {\n    text-decoration: line-through;\n    color: #999;\n    margin-right: 0.5rem;\n  }\n  \n  .hero-image {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 600px;\n    height: auto;\n    display: block;\n    margin: 2rem auto;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n  }\n  \n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .beast-launch-blog {\n      padding: 1rem;\n    }\n    \n    .blog-title {\n      font-size: 2rem;\n    }\n    \n    .features-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n  }\n</style>",
